[Student "S"]
{WEST's 3\H bid is "encouraging" so EAST bids 4NT.

When WEST shows one Key Card, (an Ace), EAST is afraid he may have a trump loser as well the 
other Ace. To find out about the \HQ he 
bids 5\D, the Queen Ask.

WEST has the \HQ but no King so she jumps 
to 6\H.}

